# More Recipes

More-Recipes is an API provides a platform for users to share the awesome and exciting recipes idea they have invented or learnt.  

# More Recipes Root [/api/v1/]

This is version 1 of the API.

# Group Users

Resources related to users in the API.

## Group User Authentication

Resources related to user authentication.

## User SignUp [/users/signup]

This action allows you to create a new account.

### Create a New Account [POST]

You may create a new account using this action. It takes a JSON object containing user details.

+ firstname (required, string) - The user's firstname.
+ lastname (optional, string) - The user's lastname.
+ username (required, unique, string) - The user's chosen username.
+ email (required, unique, string) - The user's email address.
+ password (required, string) - The user's chosen password.
+ aboutMe (optional, string) - Information about User.
+ occupation (optional, string) - The user's occupation.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "firstname": "Iveren",
            "lastname": "Shaguy",
            "username": "iverenshaguy",
            "email": "iverenshaguy@gmail.com",
            "password": "iverenshaguy",
            "aboutMe": "Food lover. Bookworm",
            "occupation": "Software Developer",
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /users/1
    
    + Body

