# Group Recipe

Resources related to recipes in the API.

## Recipes [/recipes]

A Recipe Object has the following attributes:

+ id - Recipe id
+ recipeName
+ prepTime - Recipe Preparation Time
+ cookTime - Recipe Cook Time
+ totalTime - Total Time
+ difficulty - A List of Strings to Choose from
+ extraInfo - Extra Information about Recipe
+ vegetarian - Boolean showing if suitable for vegetarians
+ ingredients - Array of ingredients
+ preparations - Array of preparation steps
+ directions - Array of direction steps
+ rating - Float of Average Recipe rating
+ likes - Array of upvotes and downvotes

