## Review a Recipe [/recipes/{recipeId}/reviews]

This action allows you review a recipe.

+ Parameters
    + recipeId: 8 (required, number) - ID of the Recipe to review in form of an integer.


### Review a Recipe [POST]

You may review a recipe using this action. It takes a JSON object containing a review.

+ rating - A number from 1 - 5 with 1 being the lowest and 5 being the highest rating (required, number)
+ comment - A comment to add to the review (string)

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "rating": 5,
            "comment": "Excellent Recipe. Loved it"
        }

